MAN: (FEEBLY) Water.

05:57.058 --> 05:58.558
Easy. Easy.

06:00.808 --> 06:03.058
Hanson here. Better send a medic out.

06:03.100 --> 06:04.933
Found one left behind. Over.

06:08.475 --> 06:09.475
(COWS MOOING)

06:15.100 --> 06:16.641
(CALLING OUT)

07:07.641 --> 07:08.808
You James Hanson?

07:09.767 --> 07:10.975
Who's asking?

07:11.017 --> 07:13.725
Carl Neeham, from Pima
County Merchants Bank.

07:17.059 --> 07:19.683
It's a Notice of Trustee's sale.

07:19.725 --> 07:22.433
Let you know that the ranch is
to be sold at auction in 90 days.

07:22.725 --> 07:23.975
What?

07:24.017 --> 07:25.767
Law requires you be notified.

07:25.808 --> 07:28.391
I'd have called, but I couldn't
find a phone listing for you.

07:28.433 --> 07:31.433
I was in last month, explained
my situation to Ned Fremont.

07:31.475 --> 07:32.683
- He assured me...
- Yes, well,

07:32.725 --> 07:34.100
Ned's no longer with us.

07:34.767 --> 07:35.975
Not sure why he didn't follow it,

07:36.017 --> 07:37.309
