08:44.725 --> 08:46.267
Well, I'm sorry to hear that.

08:46.308 --> 08:47.308
(SIGHS)

08:48.391 --> 08:50.767
I can dig that hole for you.
It'll be done by sundown.

08:55.308 --> 08:57.391
