09:05.642 --> 09:08.350
Listen, I got a new
project starting next month.

09:08.391 --> 09:10.850
Come see me then, I'll see
what I can find for you, okay?

09:12.100 --> 09:13.516
Yeah. Okay.

09:14.433 --> 09:16.433
(MOOING)

09:18.934 --> 09:21.059
MAN: I was out your way last week.

09:22.017 --> 09:23.934
