11:32.141 --> 11:33.517
What is going on?

11:34.683 --> 11:35.934
What are you doing back here?

11:40.767 --> 11:42.642
Been wondering that myself.

11:43.642 --> 11:45.975
(CHUCKLING) What the hell am I doing?

11:47.642 --> 11:50.892
